ime":"2019-12-18T07:13:49.000Z","msg":"其實除左有假放,不嬲無咩好慶祝"},{"pid":"d57a6c4b9c7d469193df1a53b99bb5da9c148a08","tid":1787749,"uid":29802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oqUDGzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoqUDGzz.jpg&h=0ea7b5bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VgwZq1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVgwZq1f.jpg&h=05719625&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ea02275924d575b40ddaffb8706c9b67c36d561","tid":1787749,"uid":36378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T07:16:27.000Z","msg":"一諗起入面班手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />重會有心情慶祝咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b039abb1ba89f9416f459d6e127f96240da445","tid":1787749,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T10:50:34.000Z","msg":"手足重要過耶穌呀！"}]}